msgid "Telegram Desktop Accessibility"
msgstr "Telegram 电脑版无障碍支持"

msgid ""
"Improves Telegram Desktop accessibility for NVDA users.\n"
"\n"
"This release fixes Tab focus entry and focus announcements for Telegram chat and message lists when Telegram exposes non-focusable UIA list containers or broken selection containers, and applies the same row protection to the phone number country selection dialog."
msgstr ""
"改善 Telegram 电脑版与 NVDA 配合使用时的无障碍体验。\n"
"\n"
"此版本修复 Telegram 暴露不可聚焦的 UIA 列表容器或损坏的选择容器时，会话列表和消息列表的 Tab 焦点进入与焦点提示无法正常朗读的问题，并将同样的列表行保护应用到电话号码国家/地区选择对话框。"

msgid "Fixed chat and message list focus speech in Telegram Desktop 6.8.3 and later by restoring focusable UIA list containers and avoiding failing selection container queries."
msgstr "通过恢复可聚焦的 UIA 列表容器并避开失败的选择容器查询，修复 Telegram 电脑版 6.8.3 及更高版本中会话列表和消息列表的焦点朗读。"
